The paper deals with iterative quantization, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of low-density generator-matrix (LDGM) codes is also a topic related to coding theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the use of density evolution (DE) and belief propagation (BP), which are topics related to statistical inference (cs.SI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
